{"tid":2360102,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"17歲義務急救員感愧疚 不斷自問「仲有咩可以做得更好」","createTime":"2021-01-09T12:12:56.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-10T12:03:54.000Z","uid":240362,"like":41,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"0d5191e274771799f4d948cc9f361f4e3f7cb030","tid":2360102,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T12:12:56.000Z","msg":"17歲義務急救員曾朗軒庭上述說梓樂墮樓那夜，緩緩吐出每字每句，彷彿每格回憶都會抽乾情緒。當人人都驚嘆於他急救時的冷靜沉著，他卻總是覺得做得不夠好。他自言「超級情緒化」，事後不知哭了多少個晚上。原本打算將傷痛交給時間，但死因庭上他將傷口剜開，鉅細靡遺地供述當晚點滴。在威權大時代下，也許拒絕遺忘、直面殘忍，是我們可做的最勇敢之事。<br />\n<br />\n回到墮樓那天，朗軒坦言第一眼看到躺在血泊中的梓樂，反應是「好嘩然、不知所措」。他憶述，梓樂傷勢極嚴重，身體多處骨折，必須盡快送院，卻久久盼不到那閃著紅藍燈的救護車，坦言感覺很無助。如今想起，他仍然耿耿於懷，「我三番四次問救護車幾時到？得到嘅回應都係『嚟緊、嚟緊、嚟緊』」。<br />\n<br />\n無法承受 只好逃避<br />\n<br />\n當晚朗軒陪梓樂到伊利沙伯醫院，逗留到清晨才離開。回家後，封存的情緒開始湧現，不敢回憶事件，最終在精神與體力不支的雙重夾擊下，沉沉睡去。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210109/DUWKF2KYOJCLJHZ25XP5XQBAAU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210109%2FDUWKF2KYOJCLJHZ25XP5XQBAAU%2F&d=3UqZ%2FPYEUq8PtOmaimGdDRfhc2i76iEVsdTpjF8%2BTp8%3D&h=b111fb67\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210109%2FDUWKF2KYOJCLJHZ25XP5XQBAAU%2F&h=50475be8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210109/DUWKF2KYOJCLJHZ25XP5XQBAAU/</a>"},{"pid":"21546e81ae5349eb914fe1faa5a5b3bb6b88668f","tid":2360102,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T12:14:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"399d5f8a665fcd7f80f3aab82aca1e4ce347141b","tid":2360102,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T12:16:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/p